data.description: This 4BR, 2.5BA home features a 3-door garage and is situated just outside the Dunn city limits in Sampson County. Highlights include engineered hardwood floors, quartz countertops, a bonus room, a downstairs bedroom, a dining room with a coffered ceiling, custom kitchen cabinets, a fenced backyard, a moisture-controlled sealed crawl space, a tankless water heater, and a Ring doorbell. The master bedroom boasts dual closets and a walk-in shower, while the laundry room is conveniently located upstairs. Nearby, there's a semi-private golf club with a pool. Enjoy the absence of HOA fees and city taxes, plus a $4,000 carpet allowance.
